<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Two-Factor Authentication Code</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .code { background: #fff; border: 2px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .code-text { font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #3498db; font-family: monospace; }
        .warning { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üîê Two-Factor Authentication</h1>
        <p>Your security code</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</h2>
        
        <p>You're attempting to sign in to your {{appName}} account. For your security, please use the verification code below:</p>
        
        <div class="code">
            <div class="code-text">{{code}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Information:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>This code expires in {{expiresIn}}</li>
                <li>Only use this code if you're trying to log in right now</li>
                <li>Never share this code with anyone</li>
                <li>If you didn't request this code, secure your account immediately</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Enter this code in your login screen to complete your sign-in process.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't attempt to sign in, someone may be trying to access your account. Please change your password immediately and contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{appName}} Security Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>